app.ui.checkAutoSolve.setChecked(False)
app.ui.checkStackImages.setChecked(True)
result = {'success': True, 'raJ2000S': Angle(hours=10), 'decJ2000S': Angle(
    degrees=20), 'angleS': 30, 'scaleS': 1, 'errorRMS_S': 3, 'flippedS': 
    False, 'imagePath': 'test', 'message': 'test'}
app.app.astrometry.signals.done.connect(app.solveDone)
with qtbot.waitSignal(app.app.message) as blocker:
    suc = app.solveDone(result=result)
    assert suc
assert ['Solved :             RA: 10:00:00 (10.000), DEC: +20:00:00 (20.000), '
    , 0] == blocker.args
